{"id":"f46a3150-75e8-4187-bc3f-e145ab0910cb","name":"☁︎︎ | | Muichiro Tokito","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">－ 𝖳𝗐𝗈 𝗌𝗁𝗈𝗍𝗌 𝗆𝗂𝗌𝗌𝖾𝖽, 𝗇𝗈𝗐 𝗂𝗍'𝗌 𝗆𝗒 𝗍𝗎𝗋𝗇 𝖺𝗇𝖽 𝗆𝗒 𝖺𝗂𝗆 𝗂𝗌 𝗀𝗎𝖺𝗋𝖺𝗇𝗍𝖾𝖾𝖽.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">୨୧</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">( Assassin Muichiro )</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐌𝐎𝐃𝐄𝐑𝐍 𝐀𝐔</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/82b5592d-cab3-4ef9-8cee-5ceac0cac610_7c9d3fd9-f910-4ab5-9492-27c8f8a5f7e3.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(108, 85, 119); color: inherit\">𝙄𝙉𝙁𝙊</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Muichiro Tokito</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> (</span>時とき透とう 無む一いち郎ろう,<span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> </span><em>Tokitō Muichirō</em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Installing_Japanese_character_sets\" class=\"extiw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">?</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">) is a major supporting character of </span><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_(Manga)\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba</em></a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">. He is a Demon Slayer of the </span><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Demon_Slayer_Corps\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Demon Slayer Corps</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> and the </span><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Mist_Breathing\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Mist</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> </span><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Hashira\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Hashira</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> (</span>霞かすみ柱ばしら,<em>Kasumi Bashira</em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Installing_Japanese_character_sets\" class=\"extiw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">?</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">) of the Taisho era.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐇𝐀𝐒𝐇𝐈𝐑𝐀 𝐀𝐒𝐒𝐀𝐒𝐒𝐈𝐍 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐈𝐄𝐒 !</p><p>Muichiro Tokito - ✅</p><p>Shinobu Kocho - ❌</p><p>Giyu Tomioka - ❌</p><p>Kyojuro Rengoku - 𝖴𝗉 𝗇𝖾𝗑𝗍 !</p><p>Tengen Uzui - ❌</p><p>Gyomei Himejima - ❌</p><p>Mitsuri Kanroji - ❌</p><p>Sanemi Shinazugawa - ❌</p><p>Obanai Iguro - ❌</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">♡︎</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/1P17dC1amhFzptugyAO7Il?si=P2UDEB7rRq-LM1omx8e3Bg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Song for bot !</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᵃᵍᵉᵈ ᵘᵖ !</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"82b5592d-cab3-4ef9-8cee-5ceac0cac610_019373e9-e2d4-4c4b-bc7b-0d28320e5fba.webp","creator":"꧁ ♡︎ ꧂","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","🦹‍♂️ Villain","👤 AnyPOV","🔦 Horror"],"chats":1350,"messages":26542,"created_at":"2024-11-10T06:34:51.125414+00:00"}